{"tid":734721,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「得罪講句」香港需要一股歧視新移民嘅風氣！！","createTime":"2018-07-09T01:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T04:32:53.000Z","uid":54226,"like":85,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd377a149d9266206d1717d66dcde570073e1e00","tid":734721,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"即使我地呢班小市民阻止唔到港共政府嘅決策<br />\n但係我哋可以由自己做起。<br />\n<br />\n當見到有新移民講蝗語嘅時候，可以試吓行過去撞鳩佢哋。之後屌返佢哋轉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外我中學發夢嗰陣試過買咗包煙，之後塞左落個新移民同學仔書包入面，再話比老師聽。希望各位中學生引以為鑑，唔好學我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b6c64f546085fdd1227d5f76cfab995bd2d798","tid":734721,"uid":54226,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"記住新移民係唔抵可憐。<br />\n我哋應該學下美國歧視黑人咁樣，歧視返新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1240dad9292d91a7e037ccfffb9f8ce101dc9f36","tid":734721,"uid":124277,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"有撚用<br />\n佢地面皮牆紙咁厚"},{"pid":"dcdfab91e65adb50746c531b493a66d02f2b1e33","tid":734721,"uid":54226,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:49:34.000Z","msg":"只少我地每個人咁做<br />\n可以形成一股歧視風氣<br />\n深化其他人對新移民嘅仇恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a709265c8d59829f0e58357eb7c21db9adf6582d","tid":734721,"uid":49258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1240dad9292d91a7e037ccfffb9f8ce101dc9f36","tid":734721,"uid":124277,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"有撚用<br />\n佢地面皮牆紙咁厚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T01:50:1